Template: wicd/notice
Type: note
_Description: Wicd clients need privileges
 As one can run scripts with root permissions from within the clients, it
 is required that some users, which will be able to run the chosen client,
 are added to the `netdev' group.

Template: wicd/users
Type: multiselect
_Choices: ${users}
Default: ${default}
_Description: Users to add to the `netdev' group
 These will be able to run the clients
